---
title: Venison Steak & Chermoula Veggie Israeli Couscous with Coriander Zhoug & Slivered Almonds
description: The delightful infusions of North African and Middle Eastern cuisine shines a little light on every aspect of this dish. And our favourite part would be the Zhoug (pronounced "Zoog")! This coriander sauce lends the dish a huge burst of flavour with punchy notes of garlic and a kick of fresh green chilli. You’ll want to drizzle it over everything soon enough.
